🔊🔊🔊 Turn up your speakers because Willy Chin has a special message just for you. 

Mark your calendars for Friday, December 15th because Willy Chin is bringing his epic birthday bash to Orlando FL, and guess what? You're invited to join the celebration! 🎉 But wait, there's a twist - it's an Ugly Sweater Edition! 🎄 

So, start scrambling through your closets and find the most festive and outrageous holiday sweaters you can. We want to see your creativity! 🎅🏿 

It all goes down at Legends Resto Lounge in Orlando FL, and trust us, Willy Chin's Birthday Bash sell off year to year! 

But here's the best part - there will be a contest for the ugliest sweater! 😂 So, bring your A-game and you might just walk away with a little something something. 😉 

From reggae to dancehall, hip-hop to soca, the vibe and atmosphere at this party will be absolutely unmatched! 

Don't miss out on this epic celebration! Save the date, grab your ugliest sweater, tell a friend and meet me by the bar dancefloor on December 15th. See you there! 🎁
Happy Birthday to me. Thank you for all the birthday wishes.  Me and my crew. 🎉
